{"title":"闲潭杂记","date":"2019-11-27T08:09:24.677Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2019年11月27日","L":"2019/11/27","MM-DD":"11-27"},"link":"2019/11/27/親啟","updated":"2019-12-12T01:08:53.235Z","content":"<p>Welcome to my miscellany!</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\">Quick Start<a href=\"2019/11/27/親啟#Quick-Start\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"Mac解决终端显示乱码\">Mac解决终端显示乱码<a href=\"2019/11/27/親啟#Mac解决终端显示乱码\"></a></h3><p>※ 打开终端的偏好设置</p>\n<p>※ 描述文件 —–》Basic —–》高级 —-》文本编码 改为Unicode（UTF-8）</p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\">Run server<a href=\"2019/11/27/親啟#Run-server\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\">Generate static files<a href=\"2019/11/27/親啟#Generate-static-files\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\">Deploy to remote sites<a href=\"2019/11/27/親啟#Deploy-to-remote-sites\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deployment</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"dailyMiscellany","link":"2019/12/10/hexo_mac部署"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/11/27/親啟/","toc":[{"title":"Quick Start","id":"Quick-Start","index":"1","children":[{"title":"Mac解决终端显示乱码","id":"Mac解决